{"tid":1536280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]其實點解唔由我地直接宣佈戒嚴","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:25:47.000Z","uid":66704,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e49438ab3d1c1d8faafe7c9c6c003353751ffd19","tid":1536280,"uid":66704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"利申：一直未出過post，有錯屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\n見今晚popo連巴士都搞埋，我一直唸緊<br />\n點解唔由我地宣佈戒嚴，而等政府話戒先戒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要說 香港政府宣佈戒嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試着說 香港已進入戒嚴狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以有文宣幫到手既話，應該大大力推到世界盡頭呢單樣<br />\n-可以twitter話俾外國知我地同戒嚴無撚分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-打共匪戰線可以係微博呃9班5毛入黎睇下香港點解折墮到要戒嚴、點知洗埋佢地腦原來popo咁恐怖，從此唔黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 係啲大商家fb/Twitter之類洗佢地版，反正平時唔留意開，等佢地以為香港真係戒左嚴， 一係就問政府係咪咁既事，或者發覺香港popo痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咁多，因為中共同政府春袋就係經濟，先唔敢戒嚴，唔敢攬炒！我地係時候幫佢一把！廣傳得夠，理論上香港經濟一定會大受挫折；大家成日話攬炒，我地就黎個攬炒預演，後果自負！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係眾志成城，第一階段應該係政府受到商家、外國關注同質疑同俾壓力，出黎澄清香港無戒嚴；但香港咁既地位出黎澄清自己無戒嚴都柒啦，唔緊要，說好一齊攬炒架嘛！亦都希望咁樣，政府先會管返班瘋狗症既人，抑制少少咪再亂咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直做開cd rom 同冷氣軍師，唔識推post亦都唔係好識寫, 但如果有志同道合既就推啦；見到無牌爛仔拉左成千幾人，為班手足極心痛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係時候到我地打輿論戰等政府知驚，而唔係好似7婆咁樣今日出黎陰陰嘴笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2801aa0c592935d3d521b6b267388cf63390f7d2","tid":1536280,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:19:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd4ec1ff3fa99e2f68095f8b05bce5c08a26fb7b","tid":1536280,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a 